| Feature      | Containers | VMs             |
| ------------ | ---------- | --------------- |
| OS           | Shared     | Separate        |
| Startup time | Seconds    | Minutes         |
| Size         | MBs        | GBs             |
| Isolation    | Medium     | Strong          |
